did.abstract: This collection consists of clippings about strikes in New York State from national and local papers made by the Albany Clipping Bureau for the School in 1946.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Clippings about strikes in New York State from national and local newspapers. This collection consists of clippings about strikes in New York State from national and local newspapers made by the Albany Clipping Bureau for the school in 1946.
